column5: Question for Simcoe experts - my friend is launching out of Talbot marina tomorrow (rental boat) and is wondering if 20km winds will make for a hairy day of fishing?  i usually only fish in cooks and will stay away when the winds get that high.  thoughts?
What direction? Thats the biggest question. I would say regardless of the forecast you may as well try, wont get anything on the couch.
They are calling E switch to SE to SES. .  East side should be ok.  Looks like a drive up to the GBAY west side in the morning for me.
